<subSubSection id="A1E247EDFFDDFFB9FF7AFDF9FB68FD40" pageId="13" pageNumber="98" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="E9471466FFDDFFB9FF7AFDF9FB68FD40" blockId="13.[151,1436,325,687]" pageId="13" pageNumber="98">
<emphasis id="DB8CC874FFDDFFB9FF7AFDF9FED9FD8B" bold="true" box="[198,312,586,612]" pageId="13" pageNumber="98">Remarks</emphasis>
. Some of the previous reports as 
<taxonomicName id="2EF86FE5FFDDFFB9FD55FDF9FC14FD8C" authorityName="Bruce" authorityYear="1969" box="[745,1013,586,611]" class="Malacostraca" family="Palaemonidae" genus="Periclimenes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="13" pageNumber="98" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="holthuisi">
<emphasis id="DB8CC874FFDDFFB9FD55FDF9FC14FD8C" box="[745,1013,586,611]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="98">Periclimenes holthuisi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are possibly incorrect. Indeed, 
<taxonomicName id="2EF86FE5FFDDFFB9FA3FFDF9FF09FD66" authorityName="Okuno &amp; Bruce" authorityYear="2010" class="Malacostraca" family="Palaemonidae" genus="Periclimenes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="13" pageNumber="98" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aqabai" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis id="DB8CC874FFDDFFB9FA3FFDF9FF09FD66" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="98">A. aqabai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="C0BF750FFFDDFFB9FF53FDC3FE92FD65" box="[239,371,624,650]" pageId="13" pageNumber="98" rank="species">comb. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, 
<taxonomicName id="2EF86FE5FFDDFFB9FE3CFDC3FDFEFD66" authorityName="Okuno &amp; Bruce" authorityYear="2010" baseAuthorityName="Okuno &amp; Nomura" baseAuthorityYear="2010" box="[384,543,624,649]" class="Malacostraca" family="Palaemonidae" genus="Ancylomenes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="13" pageNumber="98" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kobayashii" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis id="DB8CC874FFDDFFB9FE3CFDC3FDFEFD66" box="[384,543,624,649]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="98">A. kobayashii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="C0BF750FFFDDFFB9FD9BFDC3FD49FD65" box="[551,680,624,650]" pageId="13" pageNumber="98" rank="species">comb. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
and 
<taxonomicName id="2EF86FE5FFDDFFB9FD5DFDC3FC93FD66" authorityName="Okuno &amp; Bruce" authorityYear="2010" baseAuthorityName="Okuno &amp; Bruce" baseAuthorityYear="2010" box="[737,882,624,649]" class="Malacostraca" family="Palaemonidae" genus="Ancylomenes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="13" pageNumber="98" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="speciosus" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis id="DB8CC874FFDDFFB9FD5DFDC3FC93FD66" box="[737,882,624,649]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="98">A. speciosus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="C0BF750FFFDDFFB9FCC5FDC3FC1AFD65" box="[889,1019,624,650]" pageId="13" pageNumber="98" rank="species">comb. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
have been identified as 
<taxonomicName id="2EF86FE5FFDDFFB9FAABFDC3FA9CFD66" authorityName="Bruce" authorityYear="1969" box="[1303,1405,624,649]" class="Malacostraca" family="Palaemonidae" genus="Periclimenes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="13" pageNumber="98" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="holthuisi">
<emphasis id="DB8CC874FFDDFFB9FAABFDC3FA9CFD66" box="[1303,1405,624,649]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="98">holthuisi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in some scientific publications (see 
